<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <section class="hero-card">
        <header class="topbar">
          <div class="brand-wrap">
            <nav class="nav-links">
              <a class="is-active" href="#">Home</a>
              <a href="#">Projects</a>
              <a href="#">Learnings</a>
              <a href="#">Careers</a>
            </nav>

        
          </div>

          <div class="topbar-actions">
            <a class="icon-link" href="#" aria-label="Search">⌕</a>
            <a class="icon-link" href="#" aria-label="Bag">◫</a>
            <a class="icon-link" href="#" aria-label="Favorites">♡</a>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <span class="pill">Created From 20 April 2026</span>
            <h1>BLOGS</h1>
            <p>
              A bunch of blogs related to Jonathan's Activities, either it's project, learning process and Jonathan's Career

            </p>
            <div class="tech-stack" aria-label="Featured tech stack">
              <span class="stack-label">Tech stack covered</span>
              <div class="stack-icons">
                <span class="stack-chip">
                  <img
                    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/go/go-original.svg"
                    alt="Golang"
                  />
                  <span>Go</span>
                </span>
                <span class="stack-chip">
                  <img
                    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg"
                    alt="PostgreSQL"
                  />
                  <span>PostgreSQL</span>
                </span>
                <span class="stack-chip">
                  <img
                    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/redis/redis-original.svg"
                    alt="Redis"
                  />
                  <span>Redis</span>
                </span>
                <span class="stack-chip">
                  <img
                    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg"
                    alt="TypeScript"
                  />
                  <span>TypeScript</span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="hero-cta" href="#">Discover more</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-visual">
            <img
              class="hero-model"
              src="/images/jumbotron.png"
              alt="Futuristic hero model"
            />
       
             <div class="hero-title-backdrop" aria-hidden="true">Jonathan Putra</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-footer-links">
          <div class="footer-link-group">
            <a href="#">Collections</a>
            <a href="#">Designers</a>
            <a href="#">Models</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-link-group">
            <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            <a href="#">Facebook</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <main class="content">
        <section class="section-heading">
          <h2>Blog</h2>
          <p>
            Here, we share travel tips, destination guides, and stories that
            inspire your next adventure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="filters">
          <div class="filter-tabs">
            <button class="tab is-active">All</button>
            <button class="tab">Destination</button>
            <button class="tab">Culinary</button>
            <button class="tab">Lifestyle</button>
            <button class="tab">Tips &amp; Hacks</button>
          </div>

          <div class="sort-control">
            <span>Sort by:</span>
            <button class="sort-btn">Newest</button>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="post-grid">
          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-1">
              <span class="pill">Destination</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">30 Jan 2024 • 10 mins read</div>
            <h3>Unveiling the Secrets Beyond the Tourist Trails</h3>
            <p>
              Dive into the local culture, discover hidden spots, and experience
              the authentic charm that often goes unseen.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Seraphina Isabella"
              />
              <span>Seraphina Isabella</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-2">
              <span class="pill">Lifestyle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">29 Jan 2024 • 5 mins read</div>
            <h3>A Fashionista's Guide to Wanderlust</h3>
            <p>
              Explore the intersection of fashion and travel as we delve into
              the wardrobes of globe-trotters.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Maximilian Bartholomew"
              />
              <span>Maximilian Bartholomew</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-3">
              <span class="pill">Tips &amp; Hacks</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">26 Jan 2024 • 15 mins read</div>
            <h3>Top 5 Apps and Gadgets That Will Transform Your Journeys</h3>
            <p>
              Explore the latest in travel technology with our guide to must-have
              apps and gadgets.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544723795-3fb6469f5b39?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Anastasia Evangeline"
              />
              <span>Anastasia Evangeline</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-4">
              <span class="pill">Culinary</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">24 Jan 2024 • 10 mins read</div>
            <h3>Savoring Mosaic Resto Gastronomic Delights</h3>
            <p>
              From street food to fine dining, uncover the flavors that define a
              destination and the stories behind them.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Leona Pierce"
              />
              <span>Leona Pierce</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-5">
              <span class="pill">Destination</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">20 Jan 2024 • 8 mins read</div>
            <h3>Journey Through Time</h3>
            <p>
              Wander through ancient streets, visit iconic landmarks, and immerse
              yourself in the tales that shaped them.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504257432389-52343af06ae3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Elliot Navarro"
              />
              <span>Elliot Navarro</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-6">
              <span class="pill">Culinary</span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">18 Jan 2024 • 6 mins read</div>
            <h3>Experiencing Sustainable Culinary Tourism</h3>
            <p>
              Discover how mindful dining can support local communities while
              offering memorable and delicious travel moments.
            </p>
            <div class="post-author">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504593811423-6dd665756598?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80"
                alt="Maren Solis"
              />
              <span>Maren Solis</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
